titutive alterity with respect to ourselves.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aPhilosophy -- Ethics and Moral Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy -- Political Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362052040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503620520423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503620520/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles